Package ru.nsu.nrepin

Interface Graph<V,​W extends java.lang.Number>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - type of value stored in graph node
    W - type of edge weight
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdjacencyListsGraph, AdjacencyMatrixGraph, IncidenceMatrixGraph
    public interface Graph<V,​W extends java.lang.Number>
    This interface specifies behaviour for directed weighted graphs. NOTE: Terms Node and Vertex can be used interchangeably in this context. Vertices are represented with Node class.
